🌟 How to Apply Our Machine Weft Hair Extensions! 🌟

Ready to elevate your hair game with our premium machine weft hair extensions? Follow these simple steps to achieve that gorgeous, full-bodied look! 💁‍♀️✨

💖 Step-by-Step Guide:

Prep Your Hair: Start with clean, dry hair. Part your hair horizontally where you want to add the extensions.

Create a Base: Take a small section of hair along the parting line and braid it or secure it with microbeads to create a sturdy base for the weft.

Attach the Weft: Align the machine weft with the parting and sew it onto the braided base using a needle and thread or attach it with microbeads for a more temporary option.

Secure and Blend: Once the weft is securely in place, let down the top section of your hair to cover the weft. Use a flat iron or curling iron to blend your natural hair with the extensions for a seamless look.

Style as Desired: Style your hair as you normally would! Our machine weft extensions are perfect for adding volume, length, and versatility to your hairstyles.

✨ Pro Tip: Visit a professional stylist for the best results and a flawless finish!
